  componentName: Level Controller
  specifications: 
  description: "Control and monitor real-time the required water level for the calibration
    procedure on Tank 1.\r\n- Press the \u25B2 (Up) key to increase the setpoint.\r\n-
    Press the \u25BC (Down) key to decrease the setpoint.\r\n- Press ENT (Enter)
    to confirm the selected value.\r\nNote: This adjustment applies to Tank 1 only."
